  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13048987/swiss_national_day.jpg" alt="swisflag" data-udi="umb://media/bf511abf45df4d7696a5c3f23f937ac6" /></p>
<h2>Short trip or weekend ski breaks</h2>
<p>Speedy skiing in Switzerland - Short on time but big on adventure? Our flexible short ski breaks in Switzerland have you covered! Hit the slopes for as long or as short as you like.​</p>
<p>Design your perfect Swiss ski getaway! Choose your duration, departure day, hotel, and resort. Fly from your preferred airport and customise your trip with extras like ski hire and lift passes.​</p>
<p>The choice is yours, flexible durations available in 10 resorts and 35 hotels across Switzerland.​ Lift passes and ski hire is available for all booking durations. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6241eba02bd94ff394fbfd141d15a1f7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6241eba02bd94ff394fbfd141d15a1f7}" class="c-btn">View short break ski holidays</a></p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Why ski in Switzerland</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">Generally, Switzerland is considered one of the more expensive skiing destinations - but you do get what you pay for when it comes to Switzerland: </p>
<ul>
<li style="text-align: left;"><em>10 resorts</em> to choose from</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Feel extra stylish and catch a lift on the <em>Prada</em> chairlift</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Enjoy the <em>excellent quality wine</em> (and of course a couple of <em>Aperol Spritz</em> too) </li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Amazing lift system in general - <em>modern and quick</em>, no time wasted </li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Soak up those <em>once in a life-time views</em>, Switzerland mountains are another level of beautiful</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">See the <em>Toblerone mountain</em> (even if they did take it off the box)</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Enjoy some shopping in genuinely <em>beautiful towns and villages</em>, no concrete jungles here</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">We've all been to France or Austria - <em>it's time to try Switzerland</em></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn">View Switzerland</a></p>
<div> </div>
</div>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Included in your Short Break</h2>
<p>Here are some of the fantastic elements included in your short break when booking with Inghams:</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13049193/swiss-train-lp-image.jpg" alt="traintransfer" data-udi="umb://media/da2b20dfe62c449889c1bbb1c74f15b8" /></p>
<ul>
<li>2nd class return rail transfers (upgrade to 1st class if you so wish). You’ll transfer to resort by yourself, which means no waiting around at the airport for other passengers. We provide our guests with an easy, step-by-step guide to getting to your destination.<br /><span style="color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"><span></span></span></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13079676/deals-airports.jpg" alt="swisair" data-udi="umb://media/8c57dc485f8749ac8f77212a7f5196b3" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Daily departures on scheduled flights with British Airways or Swiss Airlines from our UK airports to<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/switzerland" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a></li>
<li>Half board hotel accommodation in 3, 4 and 5 star hotels, or stay on a B&amp;B basis if staying for a minimum of 3 nights</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13088875/lift-passes.jpg" alt="liftpass" data-udi="umb://media/0af17fa218444e6ba86f86118448eb0b" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Pre-bookable lift passes are also available to add to your booking and at some hotels they are included in the price of the accommodation</li>
<li><strong>FREE</strong><span> </span>ski carriage (if flying with Swiss Airlines - speak to our <a data-udi="umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193}" title="Contact Us">Reservations Team</a>)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Swiss accommodation options</h2>
<p>Here are a few examples of some of the accommodations you can book with your Inghams short breaks: </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span>Walliserhof Grand Hotel</span></h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50}" title="Saas Fee"><span>Saas Fee</span></a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13079780/walliserhof-grand-hotel-spa-artists-impression-lobby-reception.jpg" alt="walswi" data-udi="umb://media/fd937cb0bbcb4e2197f6cca4eda4abcf" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Positioned in the centre of the village and free use of the hotel shuttle service to the slopes</span></li>
<li><span>The excellent Morenia snowpark provides ample entertainment in the form of jumps and rails</span></li>
<li><span>A superb spa complete with swimming pool, sauna, steam bath, whirlpool and relaxation area</span></li>
<li><span>The hotel has three restaurants, Cäsar Ritz, Del Ponte Pizzeria and Fondue-Stübli</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><a data-udi="umb://document/e74cf27714834da9b35d5d8afce6670b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e74cf27714834da9b35d5d8afce6670b}" title="Walliserhof Grand Hotel &amp; Spa" class="c-btn">View Walliserhof Hotel</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Hotel Sport</h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b23ef1df250240c5a3657f721fdb96d0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b23ef1df250240c5a3657f721fdb96d0}" title="Klosters">Klosters</a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13086885/sport-klosters-pool.jpg" alt="hotelsport" data-udi="umb://media/ae19b7e4c77b42cab9e21fdd046e1372" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Set in its own grounds, this accommodation offers a peaceful location</span></li>
<li><span> The hotel offers a variety of leisure and extensive sports facilities</span></li>
<li><span>Klosters shares its neighbour Davos' 300km of great skiing and the full ski area is available on one pass</span></li>
<li><span>Après-ski here is relaxed, but it certainly has a few attractive bars and one or two nightclubs</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><a data-udi="umb://document/7b417118fea44c10adfbc86459d48d31" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7b417118fea44c10adfbc86459d48d31}" title="Hotel Sport" class="c-btn">View Hotel Sport</a></span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span>Hotel Alpenrose</span></h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730}" title="Wengen">Wengen</a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13103864/hotel-alpenrose-wengen-338x182.jpg" alt="HotelAlpenrose" data-udi="umb://media/54430d0945504e419442b267a352daf4" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span><span>Set on its own terrace area, the hotel enjoys views of the Lauterbrunnen Valley</span></span></li>
<li><span>Bedrooms are furnished in a modern alpine style, some have balconies and views of the valley</span></li>
<li><span>The local pass covers Wengen and Grindelwald, whilst the Jungfrau whole area pass also covers Mürren</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"><span>The hotel offers a traditional, charming</span></span> and homely lounge with log fire and bar area</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><a data-udi="umb://document/b02fd61d0fdc4c54b6515cc2162a2ae3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b02fd61d0fdc4c54b6515cc2162a2ae3}" title="Hotel Alpenrose" class="c-btn">View Hotel Alpenrose</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>Switzerland ski resorts</h2>
<p>Ski with Inghams for a short trip or weekend break to Switzerland and visit one of these amazing resorts: </p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df}" title="Davos">Davos</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/c494e0deab1140028dfcdd140d9451cc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c494e0deab1140028dfcdd140d9451cc}" title="Murren">Murren</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730}" title="Wengen">Wengen</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/0387aef01c364da3823472adfbad7c65" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0387aef01c364da3823472adfbad7c65}" title="Nendaz">Nendaz</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/313f2f0348a742b4989db3458bb4a71a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/313f2f0348a742b4989db3458bb4a71a}" title="Engelberg">Engelberg</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" title="St. Moritz">St Moritz</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/b23ef1df250240c5a3657f721fdb96d0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b23ef1df250240c5a3657f721fdb96d0}" title="Klosters">Klosters</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50}" title="Saas Fee">Saas Fee</a></li>
<li>Also consider our <a data-udi="umb://document/af62c53024f64f578d3ed3c88ddb4a9b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/af62c53024f64f578d3ed3c88ddb4a9b}" title="Lapland Short Breaks">short breaks to Lapland</a> for a quick holiday with some quality ski time. </li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>Short break skiing FAQs </h2>
<p><strong>What is the shortest break you offer?</strong> - We offer a minimum of a 3 night stay on our short breaks, short enough to go skiing for a long weekend but not too short that you wouldn't get a full days skiing or snowboarding.</p>
<p><strong>Why are your short breaks in Switzerland?</strong> - Switzerland is an ideal place for a snow-sure skiing holiday, meaning even in your short trip, you will be able to make the most of the slopes. Switzerland also has ample ski resorts to chose from so you have plenty of options and can keep revisiting one of the best countries for skiing and snowboarding alike. </p>
<p><strong>Why are transfers via rail?</strong> - Switzerland has many 'reduced traffic' or 'low carbon' towns and villages, which means rail travel helps towards this. We are very proud to offer these transfers and help Switzerland reduce it's carbon footprint as it also aligns with our <a data-udi="umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72" href="/{localLink:umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72}" title="Sustainability">sustainable journey</a>. </p>
<p> </p>
</div>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel with confidence </h2>
<p>When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png" alt="safehands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Travel, accommodation and transfers? We’ve got you covered. Book your holiday online or give us a call. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
